GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
(Department of Cabinet Affairs)
New Delhi, the 10th April 1962.
IMMEDIATE
The undersigned is directed to state that the Members
of the Council of Ministers named in the enclosed list assumed
office with effect from the forenoon of Tuesday, April 10, 1962.
(B.G. Rau )
